ActDepartment of Veterans Affairs Act
SubjectResearch Funding Program
PrecisOrder assigning to the Minister of Veterans Affairs the MANDATE to establish and implement, the RESEARCH FUNDING PROGRAM, a transfer payment program which will provide support to research initiatives benefitting the well-being of military members Veterans and their families.
